    "The performances of these ablation scenarios are shown in Table 5, categorized under the column Ablation Result.",
    "Our findings reveal that the code symbol navigation tool is particularly pivotal in our agent system.",
    "On average, CODEAGENT utilizes this tool approximately 2.45 times per code generation, a frequency higher than the counterpart of other tools.",
    "Notably, the performance significantly declines when this tool is omitted, underscoring its critical role in enhancing the effectiveness of our approach.",
    "Furthermore, the ablation results confirm that each tool in our agent system contributes positively to the overall improvement."
